y making sure the coffee industry remains viable for generations to come.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-270_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-265_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-262_ pf-heading-1-h3">Brewing a better tomorrow</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Celebrate_the_art_of_coffee_International_Coffee_Day_special_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728553848" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Celebrate_the_art_of_coffee_International_Coffee_Day_special_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728553848 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Celebrate_the_art_of_coffee_International_Coffee_Day_special_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1728553848 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Celebrate_the_art_of_coffee_International_Coffee_Day_special_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1728553848 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Celebrate_the_art_of_coffee_International_Coffee_Day_special_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1728553848 320w" width="2016" height="1344" alt="Celebrate the art of coffee International Coffee Day special - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Celebrate the art of coffee International Coffee Day special - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-266_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-268_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by astakhovyaroslav via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-264_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">As we raise our cups on International Coffee Day, let’s take a moment to reflect on the journey behind every sip and the millions of lives impacted by the coffee industry. By supporting sustainable practices